2026-04-25T13:50:52.765Z JOY-0114-F9 comment.added "Plan: (1) New joy_core::filter module with FilterSpec data struct and apply() function; move effective_milestone and is_descendant from joy-cli/ls.rs into it. (2) New joy_cli::commands::filter_args module with FilterArgs (clap Args) and to_spec(identity) -> Result<FilterSpec>; --mine resolves to populating spec.members with the current identity. (3) LsArgs replaces inline filter fields with #[command(flatten)] FilterArgs and uses joy_core::filter::apply() in place of the inline filter loop. (4) Unit tests in joy-core for every filter dimension. (5) Scope clarification: BoardArgs is intentionally NOT modified in this story to preserve the no-UX-change contract; the BoardArgs flatten plus filter application live in JOY-0116-81." [ai:claude@joy delegated-by:horst.schwarz@joydev.com]
